author: trustin
msg: Fixed issue: DIRMINA-436 (DemuxingProtocolCodecFactory doesn't reset the current MessageDecoder when NOT_OK is returned.)
* Reset currentDecoder to null when NOT_OK or wrong value is returned from the current MessageDecoder implementation.
